Founder of the INRI Evangelical Spiritual Church, Primate Elijah Ayodele, has disclosed that English Premier League club, Chelsea, is cursed and in need of spiritual cleansing. The cleric said this in a video posted on his official TikTok handle on Wednesday. READ MORE: Putin Planning Third World War With Two Other Countries – Primate Ayodele He said, “Chelsea is finished. If they are not careful they will not function again. The people who bought Chelsea should go back to the owner and get his blessings. “Otherwise if they put 10, 20 strikers, defenders, the best keeper in the world, there is a curse troubling Chelsea at this moment. I have told you, take these my words very very serious if you want to progress, otherwise Chelsea can go to total relegation.